    <h2>Day 1: Arrival in Kalimpong</h2>



    <p>Upon arrival in Kalimpong, check-in at your hotel and take some time to rest. In the afternoon, visit the following attractions:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Deolo Hill</strong> - Enjoy panoramic views of the surrounding area from this scenic viewpoint.</li>



      <li><strong>Dr. Graham's Homes</strong> - A historic educational institution with beautiful grounds.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Return to your hotel for dinner and overnight stay.</p>







    <h2>Day 2: Full Day in Kalimpong and Departure</h2>



    <p>After breakfast, embark on a full day of sightseeing in Kalimpong:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Durpin Dara Hill</strong> - Offers stunning views and is home to the Zang Dhok Palri Monastery.</li>



      <li><strong>Flower Nurseries</strong> - Visit some of the famous flower nurseries in Kalimpong.</li>



      <li><strong>Kalimpong Science Centre</strong> - A great place to learn and explore science exhibits.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Proceed to your onward journey in the evening.</p>







